replies.body:
Me during a game: "Man, I have to remember to honor this player after the game"

Me directly after closing the lobby for that game: "DAMMIT I DIDN'T HONOR THAT PLAYER"

I'm going to be really happy when they make it an in-your-face part of getting from the game back to the lobby. Also gonna be a little sad when a team is just performing exceptionally well together and I can only honor one of them ;-;
